Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rising star\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Called up by the French Federation of Basketball (FFBB) at 17, she went on to play in the national youth teams in three major tournaments, reaching the finals of the U18 European Championship and the Youth Olympic Games in 2018, and winning a gold medal at the 2019 World Beach Games.\", \"from\": 211, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 377, \"end\": 402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIBA_U18_European_Championship\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"U18 European Championship\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIBA_U18_European_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIBA_U18_European_Championship\"}, {\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Youth_Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.999999652938701, \"rank\": 3.449482519887638e-07, \"text\": \"Youth Olympic Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Youth_Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Youth_Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the French Federation\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 245}, {\"ngram\": \"Basketball\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 259}, {\"ngram\": \"FFBB\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 265}, {\"ngram\": \"the national youth teams\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"three major tournaments\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 348}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 464}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2019 World Beach Games\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time, the sky was the limit.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"the sky\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"the limit\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She moved to the United States on a full scholarship to play with UC Irvine, surpassing 1,000 points in her collegiate career after scoring a season-high 20 against UC Santa Barbara in February 2023.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 551, \"end\": 564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.695822027005199, \"rank\": 0.43713398632517003, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Damian_Irvine\", \"score\": 0.999999999569809, \"rank\": 4.2767527054986964e-10, \"text\": \"Irvine\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Damian_Irvine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Damian_Irvine\"}, {\"begin\": 699, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UC_Santa_Barbara_Gauchos\", \"score\": 0.9900550953021433, \"rank\": 0.010044784683355703, \"text\": \"UC Santa Barbara\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UC_Santa_Barbara_Gauchos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UC_Santa_Barbara_Gauchos\"}, {\"begin\": 699, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UC_Santa_Barbara_Gauchos\", \"score\": 0.9900550953021433, \"rank\": 0.010044784683355703, \"text\": \"UC Santa Barbara\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UC_Santa_Barbara_Gauchos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UC_Santa_Barbara_Gauchos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a full scholarship\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"1,000 points\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"her collegiate career\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 659}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now 24, Konate dreams of playing for France again, but it has become a trickier proposition.\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 827, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999855234829857, \"rank\": 1.4240959708178857e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Now 24, Konate dreams\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 756}, {\"ngram\": \"a trickier proposition\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What's stopping Konate from another national call-up is not her potential - it's that two years ago, she started wearing a hijab, a headscarf worn by many Muslim women to cover the hair and neck.\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999999955444765, \"rank\": 4.455515629040749e-08, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Konate\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"another national call-up\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"her potential\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 902}, {\"ngram\": \"a hijab\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"a headscarf\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 970}, {\"ngram\": \"the hair\", \"from\": 1006, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"neck\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I never thought it would be a big hindrance\\\", Konate told Al Jazeera, recalling how little changed when she started wearing it in the US at 22.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1085, \"end\": 1095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1819086897451005e-19, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}, {\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.7699988952867262, \"rank\": 0.297410192127305, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_government_of_the_United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big hindrance\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"Konate\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when she wanted to play in a tournament in France that summer, match organisers told her she could only do it if she took off her hijab.\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999855234829857, \"rank\": 1.4240959708178857e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tournament\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1215}, {\"ngram\": \"match organisers\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"her hijab\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She felt \\\"humiliated\\\", and later discovered that this was part of new FFBB regulations that forbid players from wearing \\\"any equipment with a religious or political connotation\\\".\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1376}, {\"ngram\": \"new FFBB regulations\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"any equipment\", \"from\": 1435, \"to\": 1448}, {\"ngram\": \"a religious or political connotation\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Konate felt \\\"abandoned\\\" by the FFBB and by many of her former national coaches, who never contacted her after Article 9.3 banning headscarves was implemented in December 2022.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1669, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Konate\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"the FFBB\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"her former national coaches\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"Article\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1611}, {\"ngram\": \"banning headscarves\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, Konate has turned to activism to campaign with a collective called Basket Pour Toutes (Basketball For All) that includes mostly young hijab-wearing Muslim women in France who love basketball.\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1824, \"end\": 1830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999999955444765, \"rank\": 4.455515629040749e-08, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}, {\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999855234829857, \"rank\": 1.4240959708178857e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Konate\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1682}, {\"ngram\": \"activism\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"a collective called Basket Pour Toutes\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1761}, {\"ngram\": \"Basketball\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1773}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, they are defying a hijab ban in basketball and across French sports.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1933, \"end\": 1939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9914410271608884, \"rank\": 0.00863285656665858, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hijab ban\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their campaign is gaining momentum before the Paris 2024 Olympic and Paralympic Games, as French Sports Minister Amelie Oudea-Castera announced last September that French athletes wearing a hijab will bebannedfrom competing.\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1995, \"end\": 2005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2333043982964108e-21, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2039, \"end\": 2045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9914410271608884, \"rank\": 0.00863285656665858, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2113, \"end\": 2119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9914410271608884, \"rank\": 0.00863285656665858, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their campaign\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"momentum\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1983}, {\"ngram\": \"a hijab\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Currently, any athlete wearing a hijab will be allowed to compete at Paris 2024 - except if they are French.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2244, \"end\": 2254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2333043982964108e-21, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any athlete\", \"from\": 2186, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"a hijab\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Timothee Gauthierot is a basketball club coach in the Paris suburb of Noisy-le-Sec - he is the co-founder of Basket Pour Toutes.\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2413, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2339, \"end\": 2344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.880158263370751e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2355, \"end\": 2367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Noisy-le-Sec\", \"score\": 0.9995835468665941, \"rank\": 0.0004166266387884176, \"text\": \"Noisy-le-Sec\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Noisy-le-Sec\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Noisy-le-Sec\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Timothee Gauthierot\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"a basketball club coach\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"the co\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2382}, {\"ngram\": \"founder\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"Basket Pour Toutes\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said that even before this nationwide ban, there were very few hijab-wearing girls who dreamed of becoming professional athletes in France because \\\"there is so much discrimination\\\" against them.\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999855234829857, \"rank\": 1.4240959708178857e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this nationwide ban\", \"from\": 2440, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"very few hijab-wearing girls\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"professional athletes\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2546}, {\"ngram\": \"so much discrimination\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not allow them to reach that level\\\", he said.\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that level\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Human rights experts have said the hijab ban in French basketball is part of a trend of policymakers \\\"weaponising\\\" France's tradition of la\\u00efcit\\u00e9 (secularism) to exclude Muslim women and girls from French society, drawing parallels with laws to ban the headscarf and later the abaya (loose-fitting, long-sleeved robe) in public schools,in 2004andin 2023, respectively.\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 3034, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2715, \"end\": 2721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9914410271608884, \"rank\": 0.00863285656665858, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2782, \"end\": 2788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999855234829857, \"rank\": 1.4240959708178857e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 2836, \"end\": 2842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999999955444765, \"rank\": 4.455515629040749e-08, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}, {\"begin\": 2864, \"end\": 2870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9914410271608884, \"rank\": 0.00863285656665858, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Human rights experts\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2687}, {\"ngram\": \"the hijab ban\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2711}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"a trend\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2751}, {\"ngram\": \"policymakers\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2767}, {\"ngram\": \"la\\u00efcit\\u00e9\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2811}, {\"ngram\": \"(secularism\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2823}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2858}, {\"ngram\": \"parallels\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2897}, {\"ngram\": \"laws\", \"from\": 2903, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"the headscarf\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2928}, {\"ngram\": \"later the abaya (loose-fitting, long-sleeved robe\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2982}, {\"ngram\": \"public schools\", \"from\": 2987, \"to\": 3001}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Campaigners have repeatedly pressured the FFBB to overturn Article 9.3, which was implemented without consultation from basketball clubs.\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Campaigners\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3047}, {\"ngram\": \"the FFBB\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3082}, {\"ngram\": \"Article\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3102}, {\"ngram\": \"consultation\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3150}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball clubs\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Several sources told Al Jazeera that the FFBB introduced new regulations after French senatorsvoted to banthe hijab in sporting competitions in January 2022.\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3196, \"end\": 3206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1819086897451005e-19, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}, {\"begin\": 3254, \"end\": 3260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9914410271608884, \"rank\": 0.00863285656665858, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Several sources\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3190}, {\"ngram\": \"the FFBB\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3220}, {\"ngram\": \"new regulations\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3247}, {\"ngram\": \"banthe hijab\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3290}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting competitions\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3315}, {\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 3319, \"to\": 3326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This set a precedent as attempts by acollective of Muslim women footballersto allow the hijab in French football were struck down.\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3384, \"end\": 3390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999999955444765, \"rank\": 4.455515629040749e-08, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a precedent\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3353}, {\"ngram\": \"acollective\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3380}, {\"ngram\": \"the hijab\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3426}, {\"ngram\": \"French football\", \"from\": 3430, \"to\": 3445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Rim-Sarah Alouane, a legal expert on religious freedom, said these regulations \\\"disproportionately impact Muslim women, thus amounting to indirect discrimination\\\".\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3575, \"end\": 3581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999999955444765, \"rank\": 4.455515629040749e-08, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rim-Sarah Alouane\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3486}, {\"ngram\": \"a legal expert\", \"from\": 3488, \"to\": 3502}, {\"ngram\": \"religious freedom\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3523}, {\"ngram\": \"these regulations\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3547}, {\"ngram\": \"indirect discrimination\", \"from\": 3607, \"to\": 3630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added that \\\"the principle of la\\u00efcit\\u00e9 is meant to ensure state neutrality in religious matters, not to suppress religious expression\\\".\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the principle\", \"from\": 3649, \"to\": 3662}, {\"ngram\": \"la\\u00efcit\\u00e9\", \"from\": 3666, \"to\": 3673}, {\"ngram\": \"state neutrality\", \"from\": 3693, \"to\": 3709}, {\"ngram\": \"religious matters\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3730}, {\"ngram\": \"religious expression\", \"from\": 3748, \"to\": 3768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 will be the first Olympic Games where human rights provisions are included in itsHost City Contract.\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3772, \"end\": 3782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2333043982964108e-21, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first Olympic Games\", \"from\": 3791, \"to\": 3814}, {\"ngram\": \"human rights provisions\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 3844}, {\"ngram\": \"itsHost City Contract\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 3882}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The contract states that Paris 2024 intends to \\\"guarantee respect for the human rights of all populations placed under its responsibility during the organisation\\\".\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 4048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3910, \"end\": 3920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2333043982964108e-21, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The contract\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 3897}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 3950}, {\"ngram\": \"the human rights\", \"from\": 3955, \"to\": 3971}, {\"ngram\": \"all populations\", \"from\": 3975, \"to\": 3990}, {\"ngram\": \"its responsibility\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4022}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisation\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of the Olympics, Basket Pour Toutes is pushing for both the International Olympic Committee (IOC) and the International Basketball Federation (FIBA) to intervene against France's hijab ban.\", \"from\": 4050, \"to\": 4245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4116, \"end\": 4153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4226, \"end\": 4232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999855234829857, \"rank\": 1.4240959708178857e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4059, \"to\": 4071}, {\"ngram\": \"Basket Pour Toutes\", \"from\": 4073, \"to\": 4091}, {\"ngram\": \"the International Basketball Federation\", \"from\": 4158, \"to\": 4197}, {\"ngram\": \"FIBA\", \"from\": 4199, \"to\": 4203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FIBA itself had a hijab ban until 2017, when it wasoverturnedafter an advocacy campaign.\", \"from\": 4247, \"to\": 4335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"FIBA\", \"from\": 4247, \"to\": 4251}, {\"ngram\": \"a hijab ban\", \"from\": 4263, \"to\": 4274}, {\"ngram\": \"an advocacy campaign\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the IOC allows athletes to wear headscarves in its competitions, but has not responded to letters byAmnesty International,FairSquareand theSport and Rights Alliancecalling for it to ensure France allows its hijab-wearing athletes to play sports.\", \"from\": 4336, \"to\": 4592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4351, \"end\": 4354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.201838490290911e-37, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4536, \"end\": 4542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999855234829857, \"rank\": 1.4240959708178857e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 4362, \"to\": 4370}, {\"ngram\": \"headscarves\", \"from\": 4379, \"to\": 4390}, {\"ngram\": \"its competitions\", \"from\": 4394, \"to\": 4410}, {\"ngram\": \"letters\", \"from\": 4437, \"to\": 4444}, {\"ngram\": \"byAmnesty International\", \"from\": 4445, \"to\": 4468}, {\"ngram\": \"FairSquareand theSport\", \"from\": 4469, \"to\": 4491}, {\"ngram\": \"Rights Alliancecalling\", \"from\": 4496, \"to\": 4518}, {\"ngram\": \"its hijab-wearing athletes\", \"from\": 4550, \"to\": 4576}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 4585, \"to\": 4591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For these reasons, Shireen Ahmed, an award-winning journalist focused on Muslim women in sports, said that these Olympics are the \\\"biggest case of sportswashing\\\", as France claims to protect human rights while \\\"being anti-Muslim in its own backyard\\\".\", \"from\": 4594, \"to\": 4844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4613, \"end\": 4626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shireen_Ahmed\", \"score\": 0.9999999838792065, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shireen Ahmed\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shireen_Ahmed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shireen_Ahmed\"}, {\"begin\": 4667, \"end\": 4673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999999955444765, \"rank\": 4.455515629040749e-08, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}, {\"begin\": 4760, \"end\": 4766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999855234829857, \"rank\": 1.4240959708178857e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these reasons\", \"from\": 4598, \"to\": 4611}, {\"ngram\": \"an award-winning journalist\", \"from\": 4628, \"to\": 4655}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 4683, \"to\": 4689}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 4701, \"to\": 4715}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"biggest case\", \"from\": 4720, \"to\": 4737}, {\"ngram\": \"sportswashing\", \"from\": 4741, \"to\": 4754}, {\"ngram\": \"human rights\", \"from\": 4785, \"to\": 4797}, {\"ngram\": \"its own backyard\", \"from\": 4826, \"to\": 4842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This issue is \\\"all about choice\\\" Ahmed said, describing how this ban relates to issues around women's bodily autonomy and shows an attempt by policymakers to dictate what women can or cannot wear.\", \"from\": 4846, \"to\": 5042, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This issue\", \"from\": 4846, \"to\": 4856}, {\"ngram\": \"choice\", \"from\": 4871, \"to\": 4877}, {\"ngram\": \"Ahmed\", \"from\": 4879, \"to\": 4884}, {\"ngram\": \"this ban\", \"from\": 4906, \"to\": 4914}, {\"ngram\": \"issues\", \"from\": 4926, \"to\": 4932}, {\"ngram\": \"women's bodily autonomy\", \"from\": 4940, \"to\": 4963}, {\"ngram\": \"an attempt\", \"from\": 4974, \"to\": 4984}, {\"ngram\": \"policymakers\", \"from\": 4988, \"to\": 5000}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 5017, \"to\": 5022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our objection is not with la\\u00efcit\\u00e9 [secularism], it's that it's unevenly applied,\\\" she said, noting how male athletes who wear a religious cross do not face the same scrutiny.\", \"from\": 5044, \"to\": 5219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our objection\", \"from\": 5045, \"to\": 5058}, {\"ngram\": \"la\\u00efcit\\u00e9\", \"from\": 5071, \"to\": 5078}, {\"ngram\": \"male athletes\", \"from\": 5148, \"to\": 5161}, {\"ngram\": \"a religious cross\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5188}, {\"ngram\": \"the same scrutiny\", \"from\": 5201, \"to\": 5218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the French Federation of Basketball's ban is having harsh effects on female Muslim athletes in France.\", \"from\": 5221, \"to\": 5334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5308, \"end\": 5314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999999955444765, \"rank\": 4.455515629040749e-08, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}, {\"begin\": 5327, \"end\": 5333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999855234829857, \"rank\": 1.4240959708178857e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the French Federation\", \"from\": 5232, \"to\": 5253}, {\"ngram\": \"Basketball's ban\", \"from\": 5257, \"to\": 5273}, {\"ngram\": \"harsh effects\", \"from\": 5284, \"to\": 5297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"December 4, 2022 was the date that Helene Ba was first told she was banned from playing basketball.\", \"from\": 5336, \"to\": 5435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the date\", \"from\": 5357, \"to\": 5365}, {\"ngram\": \"Helene Ba\", \"from\": 5371, \"to\": 5380}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 5424, \"to\": 5434}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ba, a 22-year-old law student who grew up in the Paris suburb of Yvelines, recalls that \\\"the most violent thing\\\" on that match day was that the referee told her coach, instead of her, that she could not play.\", \"from\": 5437, \"to\": 5645, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5486, \"end\": 5491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.880158263370751e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 5502, \"end\": 5510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yvelines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yvelines\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yvelines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yvelines\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ba\", \"from\": 5437, \"to\": 5439}, {\"ngram\": \"a 22-year-old law student\", \"from\": 5441, \"to\": 5466}, {\"ngram\": \"the most violent thing\", \"from\": 5526, \"to\": 5548}, {\"ngram\": \"that match day\", \"from\": 5553, \"to\": 5567}, {\"ngram\": \"the referee\", \"from\": 5577, \"to\": 5588}, {\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 5594, \"to\": 5603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said the referee did not even mention Article 9.3 - but instead remarked that wearing a hijab was \\\"a problem of danger\\\".\", \"from\": 5647, \"to\": 5771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the referee\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5667}, {\"ngram\": \"Article\", \"from\": 5689, \"to\": 5696}, {\"ngram\": \"a hijab\", \"from\": 5737, \"to\": 5744}, {\"ngram\": \"a problem\", \"from\": 5750, \"to\": 5759}, {\"ngram\": \"danger\", \"from\": 5763, \"to\": 5769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, knowing the law, she fought back.\", \"from\": 5773, \"to\": 5811, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the law\", \"from\": 5786, \"to\": 5793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I said that I would not take off my hijab,\\\" Ba told Al Jazeera.\", \"from\": 5813, \"to\": 5877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5866, \"end\": 5876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1819086897451005e-19, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my hijab\", \"from\": 5847, \"to\": 5855}, {\"ngram\": \"Ba\", \"from\": 5858, \"to\": 5860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"FIBA [the world basketball body] authorises it, and this was a local match.\", \"from\": 5878, \"to\": 5954, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"FIBA\", \"from\": 5879, \"to\": 5883}, {\"ngram\": \"the world basketball body\", \"from\": 5885, \"to\": 5910}, {\"ngram\": \"a local match\", \"from\": 5940, \"to\": 5953}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's violent to ask a woman to take off a piece of cloth.\", \"from\": 5955, \"to\": 6012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 5975, \"to\": 5982}, {\"ngram\": \"a piece\", \"from\": 5995, \"to\": 6002}, {\"ngram\": \"cloth\", \"from\": 6006, \"to\": 6011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a legal claim and we have the right to religion and the freedom to practice sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 6013, \"to\": 6105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a legal claim\", \"from\": 6021, \"to\": 6034}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 6047, \"to\": 6056}, {\"ngram\": \"religion\", \"from\": 6060, \"to\": 6068}, {\"ngram\": \"the freedom\", \"from\": 6073, \"to\": 6084}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 6097, \"to\": 6103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Ba said this did not stop people in the stands from asking \\\"Are you sure you do not want to take it off?\\\"\", \"from\": 6107, \"to\": 6216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ba\", \"from\": 6111, \"to\": 6113}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 6137, \"to\": 6143}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 6147, \"to\": 6157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She refused to because \\\"faith always comes first\\\", she said.\", \"from\": 6217, \"to\": 6277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 6241, \"to\": 6246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ba then left the stadium and her team played without her.\", \"from\": 6278, \"to\": 6335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ba\", \"from\": 6278, \"to\": 6280}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 6291, \"to\": 6302}, {\"ngram\": \"her team\", \"from\": 6307, \"to\": 6315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was then that Ba realised she had to do something about this, not just for her but for all Muslim athletes in France.\", \"from\": 6337, \"to\": 6457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6431, \"end\": 6437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999999955444765, \"rank\": 4.455515629040749e-08, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}, {\"begin\": 6450, \"end\": 6456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999855234829857, \"rank\": 1.4240959708178857e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ba\", \"from\": 6354, \"to\": 6356}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 6380, \"to\": 6389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you attack the freedoms of minorities, you attack everyone,\\\" Ba said.\", \"from\": 6458, \"to\": 6533, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the freedoms\", \"from\": 6475, \"to\": 6487}, {\"ngram\": \"minorities\", \"from\": 6491, \"to\": 6501}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 6514, \"to\": 6522}, {\"ngram\": \"Ba\", \"from\": 6525, \"to\": 6527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This [Article 9.3] damages the image of basketball.\\\"\", \"from\": 6534, \"to\": 6587, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the image\", \"from\": 6562, \"to\": 6571}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 6575, \"to\": 6585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Through mutual acquaintances, Ba would meet two pivotal people with whom she would co-found Basket Pour Toutes: coach Timothee Gauthierot and sociologist Haifa Tlili.\", \"from\": 6589, \"to\": 6755, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6743, \"end\": 6748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haifa\", \"score\": 0.9999999104693456, \"rank\": 8.953081381785939e-08, \"text\": \"Haifa\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haifa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haifa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mutual acquaintances\", \"from\": 6597, \"to\": 6617}, {\"ngram\": \"Ba\", \"from\": 6619, \"to\": 6621}, {\"ngram\": \"two pivotal people\", \"from\": 6633, \"to\": 6651}, {\"ngram\": \"found Basket Pour Toutes\", \"from\": 6675, \"to\": 6699}, {\"ngram\": \"coach Timothee Gauthierot\", \"from\": 6701, \"to\": 6726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After conducting more than 150 interviews with Muslim girls in sports in France, Tlili said that \\\"we do not realise the effects of these traumas\\\" triggered by the hijab ban.\", \"from\": 6757, \"to\": 6930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6804, \"end\": 6810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999999955444765, \"rank\": 4.455515629040749e-08, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}, {\"begin\": 6830, \"end\": 6836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999855234829857, \"rank\": 1.4240959708178857e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than 150 interviews\", \"from\": 6774, \"to\": 6798}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 6820, \"to\": 6826}, {\"ngram\": \"Tlili\", \"from\": 6838, \"to\": 6843}, {\"ngram\": \"the effects\", \"from\": 6873, \"to\": 6884}, {\"ngram\": \"these traumas\", \"from\": 6888, \"to\": 6901}, {\"ngram\": \"the hijab ban\", \"from\": 6916, \"to\": 6929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Many girls have told me: 'If you take basketball away from me, what do I have left?\", \"from\": 6932, \"to\": 7016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many girls\", \"from\": 6933, \"to\": 6943}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 6971, \"to\": 6981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"',\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 7016, \"to\": 7029, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Badiaga Coumba, a 21-year-old who plays in Gauthierot's club in Noisy-le-Sec, said that since the FFBB's ruling took effect, she has felt lost, unsure what to do with herself, and has pretty much given up basketball, although she considers her teammates her \\\"second family\\\".\", \"from\": 7031, \"to\": 7305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7095, \"end\": 7107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Noisy-le-Sec\", \"score\": 0.9995835468665941, \"rank\": 0.0004166266387884176, \"text\": \"Noisy-le-Sec\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Noisy-le-Sec\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympique_Noisy-le-Sec\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Badiaga Coumba\", \"from\": 7031, \"to\": 7045}, {\"ngram\": \"Gauthierot's club\", \"from\": 7074, \"to\": 7091}, {\"ngram\": \"the FFBB's ruling\", \"from\": 7125, \"to\": 7142}, {\"ngram\": \"effect\", \"from\": 7148, \"to\": 7154}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 7236, \"to\": 7246}, {\"ngram\": \"her \\\"second family\", \"from\": 7285, \"to\": 7303}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But unlike Ba, who was one of the only Muslim athletes at her club and who was left out when the hijab ban was implemented, Coumba is in a very diverse club: almost fully gender equal (rare for most basketball clubs), and with many Black and Muslim players.\", \"from\": 7307, \"to\": 7564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7346, \"end\": 7352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999999955444765, \"rank\": 4.455515629040749e-08, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ba\", \"from\": 7318, \"to\": 7320}, {\"ngram\": \"her club\", \"from\": 7365, \"to\": 7373}, {\"ngram\": \"the hijab ban\", \"from\": 7400, \"to\": 7413}, {\"ngram\": \"Coumba\", \"from\": 7431, \"to\": 7437}, {\"ngram\": \"a very diverse club\", \"from\": 7444, \"to\": 7463}, {\"ngram\": \"most basketball clubs\", \"from\": 7501, \"to\": 7522}, {\"ngram\": \"many Black and Muslim players\", \"from\": 7534, \"to\": 7563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On a team of 10 girls, there are usually three who wear the hijab, creating a strong sense of solidarity.\", \"from\": 7566, \"to\": 7671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 7569, \"to\": 7575}, {\"ngram\": \"10 girls\", \"from\": 7579, \"to\": 7587}, {\"ngram\": \"the hijab\", \"from\": 7622, \"to\": 7631}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong sense\", \"from\": 7642, \"to\": 7656}, {\"ngram\": \"solidarity\", \"from\": 7660, \"to\": 7670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When referees started telling coaches that hijab-wearing athletes could not even sit on the bench, most French clubs followed the rules - but not Coumba's club.\", \"from\": 7673, \"to\": 7833, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7777, \"end\": 7783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9914410271608884, \"rank\": 0.00863285656665858, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"referees\", \"from\": 7678, \"to\": 7686}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 7703, \"to\": 7710}, {\"ngram\": \"hijab-wearing athletes\", \"from\": 7716, \"to\": 7738}, {\"ngram\": \"the bench\", \"from\": 7761, \"to\": 7770}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 7799, \"to\": 7808}, {\"ngram\": \"not Coumba's club\", \"from\": 7815, \"to\": 7832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The eligible players went on the pitch, placed the ball on the ground, and refused to play.\", \"from\": 7835, \"to\": 7926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The eligible players\", \"from\": 7835, \"to\": 7855}, {\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 7864, \"to\": 7873}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 7882, \"to\": 7890}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 7894, \"to\": 7904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Referees would quickly grasp what was happening, and call off the match.\", \"from\": 7927, \"to\": 7999, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Referees\", \"from\": 7927, \"to\": 7935}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 7989, \"to\": 7998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gauthierot, who has stood by his female athletes when they have done this, has faced severe legal reprisals by the FFBB, and even the president of the Paris region, Valerie Pecresse.\", \"from\": 8001, \"to\": 8183, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8152, \"end\": 8157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.880158263370751e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 8166, \"end\": 8173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Little_Red_Riding_Hood\", \"score\": 0.9999999744986784, \"rank\": 2.5501706119403992e-08, \"text\": \"Valerie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Little_Red_Riding_Hood\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Little_Red_Riding_Hood\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gauthierot\", \"from\": 8001, \"to\": 8011}, {\"ngram\": \"his female athletes\", \"from\": 8030, \"to\": 8049}, {\"ngram\": \"severe legal reprisals\", \"from\": 8086, \"to\": 8108}, {\"ngram\": \"the FFBB\", \"from\": 8112, \"to\": 8120}, {\"ngram\": \"even the president\", \"from\": 8126, \"to\": 8144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On October 7, 2023, sheposted on X, formerly Twitter, \\\"I call on the State to stop leaving competition referees alone in the face of Islamist attempts to destabilise sport grounds\\\".\", \"from\": 8184, \"to\": 8365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8317, \"end\": 8325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamism\", \"score\": 0.9997172493232341, \"rank\": 0.0002645753557549872, \"text\": \"Islamist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 8187, \"to\": 8194}, {\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 8217, \"to\": 8218}, {\"ngram\": \"the State\", \"from\": 8249, \"to\": 8258}, {\"ngram\": \"competition referees\", \"from\": 8275, \"to\": 8295}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 8305, \"to\": 8313}, {\"ngram\": \"sport grounds\", \"from\": 8350, \"to\": 8363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After receiving a collective letter from 70 Paris clubs protesting this basketball hijab ban, Pecresse ordered the suspension of \\\"any subsidy to a club violating our charter of la\\u00efcit\\u00e9\\\".\", \"from\": 8367, \"to\": 8553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8411, \"end\": 8416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.880158263370751e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a collective letter\", \"from\": 8383, \"to\": 8402}, {\"ngram\": \"this basketball hijab ban\", \"from\": 8434, \"to\": 8459}, {\"ngram\": \"Pecresse\", \"from\": 8461, \"to\": 8469}, {\"ngram\": \"the suspension\", \"from\": 8478, \"to\": 8492}, {\"ngram\": \"any subsidy\", \"from\": 8497, \"to\": 8508}, {\"ngram\": \"a club\", \"from\": 8512, \"to\": 8518}, {\"ngram\": \"our charter\", \"from\": 8529, \"to\": 8540}, {\"ngram\": \"la\\u00efcit\\u00e9\", \"from\": 8544, \"to\": 8551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since most clubs are dependent on public funds, as many as 20 clubs have been heavily impacted and have had to retract their support.\", \"from\": 8555, \"to\": 8688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most clubs\", \"from\": 8561, \"to\": 8571}, {\"ngram\": \"public funds\", \"from\": 8589, \"to\": 8601}, {\"ngram\": \"as many as 20 clubs\", \"from\": 8603, \"to\": 8622}, {\"ngram\": \"their support\", \"from\": 8674, \"to\": 8687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The FFBB has also hit back directly against Gauthierot, fining him 300 euros ($325) and suspending him from all official capacities in basketball for six months from September 2024, in an ongoing case that Gauthierot is legally contesting.\", \"from\": 8690, \"to\": 8929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The FFBB\", \"from\": 8690, \"to\": 8698}, {\"ngram\": \"Gauthierot\", \"from\": 8734, \"to\": 8744}, {\"ngram\": \"300 euros\", \"from\": 8757, \"to\": 8766}, {\"ngram\": \"all official capacities\", \"from\": 8798, \"to\": 8821}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball\", \"from\": 8825, \"to\": 8835}, {\"ngram\": \"six months\", \"from\": 8840, \"to\": 8850}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 8856, \"to\": 8865}, {\"ngram\": \"an ongoing case\", \"from\": 8875, \"to\": 8890}, {\"ngram\": \"Gauthierot\", \"from\": 8896, \"to\": 8906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They say that it [the hijab] can lead to radicalisation, but we really live in harmony,\\\" Gauthierot said.\", \"from\": 8931, \"to\": 9037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hijab\", \"from\": 8950, \"to\": 8959}, {\"ngram\": \"radicalisation\", \"from\": 8973, \"to\": 8987}, {\"ngram\": \"harmony\", \"from\": 9011, \"to\": 9018}, {\"ngram\": \"Gauthierot\", \"from\": 9021, \"to\": 9031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They [the FFBB] make decisions without knowing us.\\\"\", \"from\": 9038, \"to\": 9090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the FFBB\", \"from\": 9045, \"to\": 9053}, {\"ngram\": \"decisions\", \"from\": 9060, \"to\": 9069}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 9086, \"to\": 9088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gauthierot, who is of Guadeloupean origin, cited sports legends who stood up against discrimination as role models, like modern American football'sColin Kaepernick; or former US runners Tommie Smith and John Carlos, who gave the Black Power salute at the 1968 Mexico City Olympics.\", \"from\": 9092, \"to\": 9373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9114, \"end\": 9126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guadeloupe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3559963897808794e-13, \"text\": \"Guadeloupean\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guadeloupe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guadeloupe\"}, {\"begin\": 9213, \"end\": 9237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Modern_history_of_American_football\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"modern American football\", 