ce/1968_Olympics_Black_Power_salute\", \"score\": 0.7737559506701273, \"rank\": 0.29239716881555367, \"text\": \"Black Power salute\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1968_Olympics_Black_Power_salute\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1968_Olympics_Black_Power_salute\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gauthierot\", \"from\": 9092, \"to\": 9102}, {\"ngram\": \"sports legends\", \"from\": 9141, \"to\": 9155}, {\"ngram\": \"discrimination\", \"from\": 9177, \"to\": 9191}, {\"ngram\": \"role models\", \"from\": 9195, \"to\": 9206}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1968 Mexico City Olympics\", \"from\": 9343, \"to\": 9372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have got nothing to lose,\\\" said Gauthierot, who works in IT and volunteers at the local basketball club.\", \"from\": 9375, \"to\": 9482, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 9387, \"to\": 9394}, {\"ngram\": \"Gauthierot\", \"from\": 9410, \"to\": 9420}, {\"ngram\": \"the local basketball club\", \"from\": 9456, \"to\": 9481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd rather do it without discriminating against girls.\\\"\", \"from\": 9483, \"to\": 9539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 9532, \"to\": 9537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Critics of the hijab ban point out that this is happening while France prepares to host the first Olympic Games to reachfull gender parity, making the situation even more alarming.\", \"from\": 9541, \"to\": 9721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9605, \"end\": 9611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999855234829857, \"rank\": 1.4240959708178857e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Critics\", \"from\": 9541, \"to\": 9548}, {\"ngram\": \"the hijab ban point\", \"from\": 9552, \"to\": 9571}, {\"ngram\": \"the first Olympic Games\", \"from\": 9629, \"to\": 9652}, {\"ngram\": \"gender parity\", \"from\": 9666, \"to\": 9679}, {\"ngram\": \"the situation\", \"from\": 9688, \"to\": 9701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"By proudly claiming that the Games will be 'gender equal', the French authorities are exposing their own hypocrisy of celebrating such alleged advancements while at the same time discriminating against Muslim women and girls through hijab bans in sports,\\\" Amnesty International researcher Anna Blus said.\", \"from\": 9723, \"to\": 10028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9787, \"end\": 9793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9914410271608884, \"rank\": 0.00863285656665858, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 9926, \"end\": 9932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.999999955444765, \"rank\": 4.455515629040749e-08, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}, {\"begin\": 9980, \"end\": 10001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amnesty_International\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0557111448639332e-28, \"text\": \"Amnesty International\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amnesty_International\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amnesty_International\"}, {\"begin\": 10013, \"end\": 10017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"score\": 0.9999999968786142, \"rank\": 3.1204708581634835e-09, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 9749, \"to\": 9758}, {\"ngram\": \"their own hypocrisy\", \"from\": 9819, \"to\": 9838}, {\"ngram\": \"such alleged advancements\", \"from\": 9854, \"to\": 9879}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 9889, \"to\": 9902}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 9943, \"to\": 9948}, {\"ngram\": \"hijab bans\", \"from\": 9957, \"to\": 9967}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 9971, \"to\": 9977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Andrea Florence, director of the Sports & Rights Alliance, highlighted, \\\"It's the Olympic principle 6 [ofthe Olympic Charter] that people should enjoy sports without discrimination of any kind.\", \"from\": 10030, \"to\": 10223, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10037, \"end\": 10045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florence\", \"score\": 0.9999988825390451, \"rank\": 1.1174620446373132e-06, \"text\": \"Florence\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florence\"}, {\"begin\": 10079, \"end\": 10087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alliance_Party_of_Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9997976578254881, \"rank\": 0.00020238312481981309, \"text\": \"Alliance\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alliance_Party_of_Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alliance_Party_of_Northern_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"director\", \"from\": 10047, \"to\": 10055}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic principle\", \"from\": 10108, \"to\": 10129}, {\"ngram\": \"[ofthe Olympic Charter\", \"from\": 10132, \"to\": 10154}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 10161, \"to\": 10167}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 10181, \"to\": 10187}, {\"ngram\": \"discrimination\", \"from\": 10196, \"to\": 10210}, {\"ngram\": \"any kind\", \"from\": 10214, \"to\": 10222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not about the number of people banned, it's about those who can not even be included.\\\"\", \"from\": 10224, \"to\": 10315, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 10239, \"to\": 10249}, {\"ngram\":